The MCP server answers questions from its own built-in text — no AI calls, no API keys, no monthly bills.

---

## Glossary

**MCP** — Model Context Protocol. A standard that lets AI assistants connect to external tools.

**SSE** — Server-Sent Events. The technology the MCP server uses to stay connected to an AI assistant in real time.

**Vercel** — A hosting platform. Runs your code and gives it a public URL. Free for projects like this.

**Serverless function** — The way Vercel runs `api/mcp.js`. It spins up when a request comes in and shuts down after. No server to manage.

**MCP endpoint** — The URL (`/sse`) that AI assistants connect to. Think of it as a door the AI knocks on.

